headline: 3 Big Reasons ADSK Should Be On Your Watchlist
summary: Autodesk’s 25.7% return over the past six months has outpaced the S&P 500 by 13.1%, and its stock price has climbed to $300.87 per share. This was partly due to its solid quarterly results, and the performance may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
